    <briefdescription>
<para>Lightweight table-driven finite state machine. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Define states and events as enums, then describe transitions in a const table. The FSM dispatches events, calls transition actions, and optionally logs every transition via the logging module.</para>
